<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Curtle-axe" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Curtle-axe,</orth> cutlass, a broad, curving sword: <cit><quote>a gallant c. upon my thigh,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.119" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 3, 119</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>scarce blood enough to give each naked c. a stain,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 2, 21</bibl></cit>.
